#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about teen safety.\n"
"\n"
"Teens can spend a lot of time outside the house or online, where it is harder for us to keep them safe.\n"
"\n"
"Talking together about safe and unsafe places, and how to prevent problems, really helps!"
msgstr ""
"Mada ya leo ni  kuhusu usalama wa vijana.\n"
"\n"
"Vijana wanaweza kutumia muda mwingi nje ya nyumba au mtandaoni, ambako ni vigumu kwetu kuwaweka salama.\n"
"\n"
"Kuzungumza pamoja kuhusu maeneo salama na yasiyo salama, na jinsi ya kuzuia matatizo, husaidia sana!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why is teen safety important for you and your family?"
msgstr "Kwanini usalama wa vijana ni muhimu kwako na familia yako?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today our topic is teen safety.\n"
"\n"
"It is our responsibility as parents to keep our teens safe at all times. We need to ensure that our teenagers are safe in the communities that we live in. It is our responsibility that we make them aware of the safe and unsafe areas in the communities.\n"
"\n"
"It is also our responsibility to ensure that they understand the dangers that they might be exposed to when they are online. That way our teenagers will be responsible and be able to make right decisions to keep themselves safe too."
msgstr ""
"Habarini, wote.\n"
"\n"
"Mada yetu ni usalama wa vijana.\n"
"\n"
"Ni jukumu letu kama wazazi kuhakikisha kuwa vijana wetu wako salama wakati wote. Tunahitaji kuhakikisha kwamba vijana wetu wako salama katika jamii tunazoishi. Ni jukumu letu kuwafanya watambue maeneo salama na yasiyo salama katika jamii.\n"
"\n"
"Ni jukumu letu pia kuhakikisha kuwa wanaelewa hatari wanazoweza kukumbana nazo wanapokuwa mtandaoni. Kwa njia hiyo, vijana wetu watakuwa na uwajibikaji na wataweza kufanya maamuzi sahihi ya kujilinda wao wenyewe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes our teens know things about their environment that we might not realise - and by talking, we can learn how to support them better."
msgstr "Wakati mwingine vijana wetu wanajua mambo kuhusu mazingira yao ambayo huenda sisi hatufahamu ‚Äì na kwa kuzungumza nao, tunaweza kujifunza jinsi ya kuwasaidia vyema zaidi.."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A safety plan helped @data.characters.media_female_8.name protect her teen. Tap play to hear more"
msgstr "Mpango wa usalama ulimsaidia @data.characters.media_female_8.name  kumlinda  kijana wake. Bonyeza kusikiliza zaidi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I was so grateful to make the safety plan with my teen. I thought I knew which areas are safe for my teen and which are not. But when we made the safety plan together, I realised that my girl knew more areas that I was not aware of.\n"
"\n"
"I also thought she was safe at school, but through this activity I realised she was being bullied and the teachers did not do anything about it.\n"
"\n"
"The more we talked, the more I understood and got information from my teen. That really helped me to protect my teen and keep her safe."
msgstr ""
"Nilifurahi sana kuandaa mpango wa usalama pamoja na kijana wangu. Nilidhani ninajua maeneo salama kwa kijana wangu na yale ambayo si salama. Lakini tulipoandaa mpango wa usalama pamoja, niligundua kwamba binti yangu alijua maeneo mengi zaidi ambayo mimi sikuwa nayajua.\n"
"\n"
"Nilidhani pia kuwa yuko salama shuleni, lakini kupitia shughuli hii niligundua kwamba alikuwa ananyanyaswa na walimu hawakufanya chochote kuhusu hilo.\n"
"\n"
"Kadri tulivyozungumza zaidi, ndivyo nilivyoelewa zaidi na kupata taarifa kutoka kwa kijana wangu. Hilo lilinisaidia sana kumlinda kijana wangu na kumuweka salama."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name:
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"The most important way to help keep your teen safe is to make sure that they know they can talk to you about anything. \n"
"\n"
"You can also come up with a Safety Word - a simple word your teen can use to let you know they have a problem, without fear of you getting angry. \n"
"\n"
"Let's see how this worked for @data.characters.f1_mother.name and her daughter @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name:"
msgstr ""
"Njia muhimu zaidi ya kusaidia kumlinda kijana wako ni kuhakikisha wanajua kuwa wanaweza kuzungumza nawewe kuhusu chochote.\n"
"\n"
"Pia unaweza kuanzisha Neno la Usalama ‚Äì neno rahisi ambalo kijana wako anaweza kutumia kukuambia kuwa ana tatizo, bila hofu ya kukukasirisha.\n"
"\n"
"Acha tuone hii ilivyofanya kazi kwa @data.characters.f1_mother.name na mtoto wake  @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name:\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
