#.      @data.characters.friend_female_1.name!
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Something happened when I was out with my friends @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name and @data.characters.friend_female_1.name!"
msgstr "Kuna kitu kilitokea nilipokuwa tumetoka na marafiki zangu @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name na @data.characters.friend_female_1.name!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tell me, @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name."
msgstr "Niambie, @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hey beautiful. I have been looking at you for a while. You are very beautiful, what is your name?"
msgstr "Heyi mrembo. Nimekuwa nikikuangalia kwa muda sasa. Umeonekana ni mzuri sana, jina lako ni nani?\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Her name is @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name."
msgstr "Jina lake ni @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name, would you like to come with me to have something to drink and chips? Come on, get in, you will be back in time, I promise‚Ä¶"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name Je, ungependa kwenda  pamoja nami kupata kinywaji na kula chipsi? Njoo, ingia, utarudi kwa wakati, nakuahidi‚Ä¶\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am not sure if that is a good idea‚Ä¶"
msgstr "Sina hakika kama hilo ni wazo zuri‚Ä¶"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You are lucky, my friend. I wish a man would ask ME out and buy me gifts. I am telling you, if you do not do this I‚Äôm going to tell everyone you are stupid!"
msgstr "Una bahati, rafiki yangu. Natamani mwanaume angeniomba nikutane naye na kununulia zawadi. Nakwambia, kama hutafanya hivi nitamwambia kila mtu kuwa wewe ni mjinga!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name do not go! Be careful! Let‚Äôs go home. It is dangerous to go with people you do not know. Besides, he is too old for you and what he is doing is wrong."
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name Usiende! Jihadhari! Twende nyumbani. Ni hatari kwenda na watu usiowafahamu. Ukiacha hayo, yeye ni mzee mno kwako na kile anachokifanya si sahihi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I just do not know‚Ä¶"
msgstr "Yaani sijui‚Ä¶"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Pfff, I am so proud of you for not getting into the car. That was a dangerous situation, thank you for telling me!\n"
"\n"
"You can always call me or talk to me when something like this happens. We can even use a Safety Word, so I know something is wrong - and I promise I will not be angry."
msgstr ""
"Pfff, najivunia sana kwamba hujakaa kwenye gari. Hiyo ilikuwa hali hatari, asante kwa kuniambia!\n"
"\n"
"Wakati wote unaweza kunipigia simu au kuzungumza nami wakati kitu kama hiki kinapotokea. Tunaweza hata kutumia Neno la Usalama, ili nijue kuna tatizo ‚Äì na naahidi sitakasirika.\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you, @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name! Our Safety Word could be ‚Äòblue house‚Äô. I could call and say something like ‚ÄòI forgot my book at the blue house‚Äô and you would know to come help me."
msgstr ""
"Ahsante, @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name\n"
"Neno letu la Usalama linaweza kuwa ‚Äònyumba ya bluu‚Äô. Ningeweza kupiga simu na kusema kitu kama ‚ÄòNimesahau kitabu changu kwenye nyumba ya bluu‚Äô na utajua kuja kunisaidia."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about what happened to @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name."
msgstr "Hebu tufikirie kuhusu kilichotokea kwa@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What was risky about that situation?"
msgstr "Kitu gani kilikuwa cha hatari kwenye tukio hilo?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The man in the car was pressuring @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name with gifts"
msgstr ""
"Mwanaume aliyekuwa kwenye gari alikuwa anamlazimisha\n"
"@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name kwa zawadi\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name's friend was encouraging her"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name rafiki  alikuwa anamhimiza\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Going with an older man puts @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name in a dangerous situation where she can get hurt or be forced to do things"
msgstr "Kuenda na mwanaume mwenye umri mkubwa kunamuweka @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name katika hali ya hatari ambapo anaweza kuumizwa au kulazimishwa kufanya vitu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Many girls in our communities get pregnant or catch HIV from older men"
msgstr "Wasichana wengi katika jamii zetu wanapata mimba au kuambukizwa VVU na wanaume wenye umri mkubwa"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "There were no other trusted adults to advise @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name"
msgstr "Hakukuwa na watu wazima wa kuaminika walioweza kumpa ushauri @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"All those things are true! \n"
"\n"
"@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name could have gotten into a dangerous situation if she had gotten into the car."
msgstr ""
"Mambo yote hayo ni ya kweli!\n"
"\n"
"@data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name angeweza kujikuta katika hali ya hatari kama angeingia kwenye gari."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's look at another example of a dangerous situation together."
msgstr "Hebu tuangalie pamoja mfano mwingine wa tukio la hatari."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My friend has been talking with a guy our age online... She is going to send him photos of herself. Is that better because he is our age?"
msgstr "Rafiki yangu amekuwa akizungumza na mvulana wa rika letu mtandaoni... Anataka kumtumia picha zake. Je, hiyo ni vizuri kwa sababu ni wa umri wetu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"You are a good friend for being worried about her. Sending sexy photos is a real risk too.\n"
"\n"
"Sometimes people are not who they say they are online ‚Äì he could say he is your age but be a 50-year-old man. Or when they break up, he could send those photos to everyone and your friend would feel awful."
msgstr ""
"Wewe ni rafiki mzuri kwa kuwa na wasiwasi juu yake. Kutuma picha za kihisia au za utupu ni hatari kubwa pia.\n"
"\n"
"Wakati mwingine watu si kama wanavyosema wanavyokuwa mtandaoni ‚Äì anaweza kusema ana umri wako lakini ni mwanaume mwenye miaka 50. Au wakati wanapoachana, anaweza kutuma picha hizo kwa kila mtu na rafiki yako atahisi vibaya sana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Things like that can happen to any teen, so let's think about our teens' online safety."
msgstr "Mambo kama hayo yanaweza kutokea kwa kijana yeyote, kwa hiyo hebu tufikirie kuhusu usalama wa vijana wetu mtandaoni. "

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What do you think is the biggest online risk for teens these days?"
msgstr "Unadhani ni hatari gani kubwa zaidi mtandaoni kwa vijana siku hizi?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Adults use social media, gaming and messaging apps and websites to meet teenagers and pressure them to do sexual things"
msgstr "Watu wazima hutumia mitandao ya kijamii, michezo ya mtandaoni, na programu za ujumbe pamoja na tovuti kukutana na vijana na kuwashinikiza kufanya mambo ya ngono"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, this is a serious risk. Some adults may act friendly online but try to trick or pressure teens. Talking openly can help keep your teen safe."
msgstr "Ndiyo, hii ni hatari kubwa sana. Watu wazima wengine wanaweza kuonyesha urafiki mtandaoni lakini wanajaribu kudanganya au kuwatia shinikizo vijana. Kuzungumza kwa uwazi kunaweza kusaidia kumlinda kijana wako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "People post things online to make us hurt other people - like making violence seem cool or spreading hate towards certain races or countries"
msgstr "Watu huweka vitu mtandaoni ili kutufanya tuumize watu wengine ‚Äì kama kufanya ukatili kuwa jambo la kuvutia au kueneza chuki dhidi ya rangi fulani au nchi nyingine\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, this is a real concern. Some people spread hate or make violence seem normal. Helping your teen think about what they see online can protect them."
msgstr "Ndiyo, hili ni jambo la kweli la wasiwasi. Watu wengine hueneza chuki au kufanya ukatili kama jambo la kawaida. Kumsaidia kijana wako kufikiria kuhusu wanachoona mtandaoni kunaweza kumlinda."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "People put things online to convince teenagers to hurt themselves or take their own lives"
msgstr "Watu huweka vitu mtandaoni kuwahamasisha vijana kujiua au kujihatarisha kwa kuumiza nafsi zao\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, sadly this does happen. Some online spaces can make teens feel hopeless or alone. Checking in often can help keep your teen safe."
msgstr "Ndiyo, kwa bahati mbaya hili hufanyika. Baadhi ya maeneo mtandaoni yanaweza kufanya vijana wajisikie kukata tamaa au upweke. Kuangalia mara kwa mara kunaweza kusaidia kumlinda kijana wako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Teenagers share sexy photos, videos or information about themselves, and others use it to embarrass or threaten them"
msgstr "Vijana hutuma picha za kingono, video au taarifa zao binafsi, na wengine hutumia hizo kuwaaibisha au kuwatishia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, this is a real danger. Once something is shared, it can be spread or used to hurt them. Teaching your teen to pause and think before sharing can make a big difference."
msgstr "Ndiyo, hii ni hatari kubwa. Mara tu kitu kinapotumwa kwa wengine, kinaweza kusambazwa au kutumiwa kuwadhuru. Kumfundisha kijana wako kusimama kidogo na kufikiria kabla ya kutuma kwa watu wengine kunaweza kufanya tofauti kubwa.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "People can often be nasty to teenagers online - they feel like they can bully people safely"
msgstr "Watu mara nyingi huwa wabaya kwa vijana mtandaoni ‚Äì wanahisi kama wanaweza kuwanyanyasa watu kwa usalama\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, online bullying happens a lot because people feel braver behind a screen. Talking about kindness and bullying can help your teen feel supported and know what to do."
msgstr "Ndiyo, unyanyasaji mtandaoni hutokea sana kwa sababu watu huhisi ujasiri zaidi wakiwa hawaonekani moja kwa moja. Kuzungumza kuhusu utu na unyanyasaji kunaweza kumsaidia kijana wako ajisikie kuwa na msaada na ajue cha kufanya."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"To keep our teens safe, we need to understand the dangerous situations they could get into! \n"
"\n"
"Let‚Äôs get practical now, and draw two maps of safe and unsafe places:\n"
"- üó∫Ô∏è A map of our community\n"
"- üåê A map of apps/websites we use online"
msgstr ""
"Kuwalinda vijana wetu, tunahitaji kuelewa hali hatari ambazo wanaweza kujikuta ndani yake!\n"
"\n"
"Hebu tuanze kwa vitendo sasa, na tuchore ramani mbili za maeneo salama na yasiyo salama:\n"
"- üó∫Ô∏è Ramani ya jamii yetu\n"
"- üåê Ramani ya programu/tovuti tunazotumia mtandaoni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you make these maps together with your family now?"
msgstr "Unaweza kutengeneza ramani hizi pamoja na familia yako sasa hivi?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, my family can join in now"
msgstr "Ndio, familia yangu inaweza kujiunga sasa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let me try it out by myself"
msgstr "Ngoja niijaribu peke yangu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Great! You will need a:\n"
"\n"
"- üìÑ Piece of paper (or old newspaper or a cardboard box) \n"
"- üñäÔ∏è Pen"
msgstr ""
"Vizuri! Utahitaji:\n"
"\n"
"- üìÑ Kipande cha karatasi (au gazeti la zamani au sanduku la makaratasi)\n"
"- üñäÔ∏è Kalamu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 1: Draw all the important places in your community."
msgstr "Hatua ya 1: Chora maeneo yote muhimu katika jamii yako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Draw a map of your teen‚Äôs community, with pictures of all the main places like streets, your house, school, shops, places your teen visits."
msgstr "Chora ramani ya jamii ya kijana wako, ukiwa na picha ya maeneo yote makuu kama vile barabara, nyumba yenu, shule, maduka, na sehemu ambazo kijana wako hutembelea."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 2: Choose which places are safe and unsafe."
msgstr "Hatua ya 2: Chagua ni maeneo gani ni salama na ni yapi si salama.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"- Which areas on your map are safe for teenagers? CIRCLE these\n"
"- Which areas on your map are unsafe for teenagers? CROSS those off\n"
"- What makes a place safe or unsafe?\n"
"- What could you and your teen do to keep your teen safer?"
msgstr ""
"- Ni maeneo gani kwenye ramani yako ni salama kwa vijana? ZUNGUSHIA DUARA\n"
"- Ni maeneo gani kwenye ramani yako si salama kwa vijana? YAWEKEE ALAMA YA MKASI \n"
" -Ni nini hufanya eneo liwe salama au lisilo salama?\n"
"- Ni mambo gani wewe na kijana wako mnaweza kufanya ili kumweka kijana wako salama zaidi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 3: Identify where you can get support."
msgstr "Hatua ya 3: Tambua mahali unapoweza kupata msaada."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Sometimes, we can find ourselves in trouble.\n"
"\n"
"- Where can you and your teen get support when you face a crisis? MARK those areas with a little object like a stone or piece of paper."
msgstr ""
"Wakati mwingine, tunaweza kujikuta kwenye matatizo.\n"
"\n"
"- Wapi wewe na kijana wako mnaweza kupata msaada mnapokutana na hali ya tatizo? WEKA ALAMA kwenye maeneo hayo kwa kutumia kitu kidogo kama jiwe au kipande cha karatasi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 4: Now recognise the risky places online and how you can make them safer."
msgstr "Hatua ya 4: Sasa tambua maeneo hatarishi mtandaoni na jinsi unavyoweza kuyafanya yawe salama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"- Draw pictures of the apps and websites your teenagers use\n"
"- Recognise how good they are at using the web!\n"
"- Think about which ones might be unsafe. Why?\n"
"- What could you and your teen do to make using the internet safer for your teen and their friends?"
msgstr ""
"- Chora picha za programu na tovuti ambazo vijana wako hutumia\n"
"- Tambua jinsi wanavyofahamu kutumia mtandao vizuri!\n"
"- Fikiria ni zipi ambazo zinaweza kuwa hatarishi. Kwa nini?\n"
"- Ni nini wewe na kijana wako mnaweza kufanya ili kufanya matumizi ya intaneti kuwa salama zaidi kwa kijana wako na marafiki zake?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some skills to help you keep your teen safe!"
msgstr "Hapa kuna baadhi ya ujuzi utakao kusaidia kumlinda kijana wako salama!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "MAPS"
msgstr "RAMANI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make maps with your teen of safe and unsafe areas in your community and online. Talk about how to keep their information, photos and videos private online. Talk about how once something goes online, it stays there forever. They might know an example from their friends."
msgstr "Tengeneza ramani na kijana wako juu ya maeneo salama na yasiyo salama kwenye jamii yenu na mtandaoni. Zungumzieni jinsi ya kuweka taarifa zao, picha na video zake ziwe za faragha mtandaoni. Zungumzieni jinsi ambavyo kitu kikishawekwa mtandaoni, kitakaa hapo daima. Wanaweza kujua mfano kutoka kwa marafiki zao."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "RULES"
msgstr "SHERIA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make rules with your teen about how they can stay safe in your community (especially in risky areas that cannot be avoided), and how they can safely use the apps and websites that they like."
msgstr "Tengeneza sheria na kijana wako kuhusu jinsi ya kujilinda katika jamii yenu (hasa katika maeneo hatari ambayo hayaepukiki), na jinsi wanavyoweza kutumia kwa usalama programu na tovuti wanazozipenda."

