msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember how @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name and her mother, @data.characters.f1_mother.name, made a rule together to help @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name have fun and stay safe online? It worked well because they made clear rules together in a calm and positive way!"
msgstr "Kumbuka jinsi @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name na mama yake, @data.characters.f1_mother.name, walivyotengeneza sheria pamoja kusaidia @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name awe na ufuraha na kuwa salama mtandaoni! Ilifanikiwa vizuri kwa sababu walitengeneza sheria wazi kwa pamoja kwa njia tulivu na chanya!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SAFETY WORD"
msgstr "NENO LA USALAMA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Agree on a Safety Word. If something happens that makes your teen upset, uncomfortable or scared, they can say the Safety Word and you will help them without getting angry or punishing them, even if they were doing something wrong."
msgstr "Kukubaliana juu ya Neno la Usalama. Ikiwa kutatokea jambo lolote litakalomfanya kijana wako kuhisi huzuni, wasiwasi au hofu, anaweza kusema Neno la Usalama na utamsaidia bila kuchukizwa au kumwadhibu, hata kama alikuwa anafanya kitu kisicho sahihi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Vidokezo zaidi"

#. type=data_list
